en_127599_0	The JPV expects to file a petition with the Supreme Court soon requesting the Top Court to order the Government to empower the Paddy Marketing Board Act.
en_127599_1	Chairman of the JVP affiliated All Ceylon Farmers Federation and North Western Provincial Councilor Namal Karunarathna stated this during a media conference held in Dambulla yesterday.
en_127599_2	He further said that the ministry will be cordoned with the participation of farmers if their problems are not attended to in the near future.
